{"tid":1626612,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"期待手持午餐肉有閪屌既日子～～","createTime":"2019-10-05T12:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T12:15:23.000Z","uid":54728,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"78a8c3504d1ab0e3f8c87f793fa3170eb3c9b2de","tid":1626612,"uid":54728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:04:40.000Z","msg":"2012又好,927又好,UFO又好,有咩事發生都唔驚,,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1zBfCq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1zBfCq.jpg&h=e6f47af5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUcCKvU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUcCKvU.jpg&h=7691ca2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v9n7nhE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv9n7nhE.jpg&h=4e259193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3d7301d5cfc83839489310475ddf44ac888f49","tid":1626612,"uid":54728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:06:37.000Z","msg":"唔記得改日子..."},{"pid":"8c19decc74e960aa1cf0e2dd080886d4a618e860","tid":1626612,"uid":152147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b3d7301d5cfc83839489310475ddf44ac888f49","tid":1626612,"uid":54728,"like":